content:
Enable Einstein Conversation Mining in minutes. 

REQUIRED EDITIONS AND USER PERMISSIONS: 
Available in: Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions.

USER PERMISSIONS NEEDED:
Customize Application
OR
Modify Metadata
OR
Manage Bots

Turn on Einstein Conversation Mining.
(Optional) To get reports, turn on Connect to Data Cloud.
Your data can take up to 1 hour to process before you can start building an Enhanced Conversations report.
title: Enable Einstein Conversation Mining in Service Cloud
